Program: Great Lives
Title: Paul Robeson
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00b1czw
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Jan 2017
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. Anna Ford nominates singer, actor and civil rights activist Paul Robeson. From Shakespeare to Showboat, his success as a stage actor was matched by his popularity as a singer, until he fell foul of the House of Un-American Activities Committee. Show less